## Dev Env

- WSL2(networkingMode = bridged) + Docker-Desktop
  - `.wslconfig`: tested with `networkingMode = bridged`
- Python 3.11 venv

  ```bash
  ### Option-1: with uv
  uv venv --python 3.11 --seed

  ### Option-2: with pip
  python3.11 -m venv .venv
  source .venv/bin/activate
  pip install -U pip
  ```

